{"tid":1721351,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發｜參院剛啟動「熱線」機制 六小時內無人反對即通過《法案》】","createTime":"2019-11-14T15:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T21:30:25.000Z","uid":205927,"like":149,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"fb8ca72f1ae281c0417d91fca2fba9389c62cb64","tid":1721351,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:39:08.000Z","msg":"剛剛習近平在金磚國家領導人會晤上，提出「止暴制亂是香港當前最緊迫的任務」、恐嚇香港人之際，同一時間，美國國會再度出手。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志駐華盛頓代表敖卓軒收到消息，得悉Mitch McConnell剛剛將《法案》提交參議院審議，並啟動「熱線」（hotline）機制。<br />\n<br />\n在「熱線」機制下，《法案》提交後六小時內（即香港時間星期五凌晨5點前），沒有參議員反對的話，就當作參議院一致通過，法案就會明早交到白宮處理。<br />\n<br />\n希望今次冇人阻住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78e9d0279851978d22f96c05f67cd3835bce306","tid":1721351,"uid":190793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:40:14.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3af95ddae10452976f334f7dad32da092a69d2da","tid":1721351,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:40:21.000Z","msg":"要加辣先有用"},{"pid":"47422227ea3a27a432a5fad34402d948ca673d71","tid":1721351,"uid":12423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:41:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fdc5b29141ab98aeb90b3fd484132b873c0c735b","tid":1721351,"uid":283204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:41:03.000Z","msg":"要推"},{"pid":"67162f8b3af429a659b170f5c85cf3a1cc676a1b","tid":1721351,"uid":235015,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:41:08.000Z","msg":"邊個反對就...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6158509b9b7fa599a38e34aa0b1590f1c5b4bb","tid":1721351,"uid":143569,"